al Links = | Special Notes = }} [[File:Kawayu hot spring river.jpg|thumb|200px|right|Hot spring river flowing through the hot spring town]] [[File:川湯温泉駅足湯.jpg|thumb|200px|right|Foot bath at {{ill|Kawayu-Onsen Station|en|Kawayu-Onsen Station|qid=Q6379906|lt=Kawayu Onsen Station|1=Kawayu-Onsen Station}}]] '''Kawayu Onsen''' (川湯温泉) is a {{ill|Onsen|en|Onsen|qid=Q655311|lt=Onsen|1=Onsen}} located in {{ill|Hokkaido|en|Hokkaido|qid=Q35581|lt=Hokkaido|1=Hokkaido}}, {{ill|Teshikaga, Hokkaido|en|Teshikaga, Hokkaido|qid=Q1186104|lt=Teshikaga Town|1=Teshikaga, Hokkaido}}. Its name is an Ainu translation of “セセキ（hot）ペツ（river）.” A high-temperature hot spring river flows through the town.
